Class Musician

  • java.lang.Object
    • Artist
      • Musician

  • public class Musician
extends Artist

    This class extends the class Artist. By doing this this class can make use of all the properties inherited and can be set in the constructor of this class.

    The method toString is being overridden to change it's functionality and output only what it needs to output.

    Alexander Chetcuti
